@startuml session_continue_flow
title Session Continue (Phase 2b) — Extend Idle Time Without Banking

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceArrowFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceParticipantPadding 20

actor "Customer" as C
participant "ATM UI\n(Flask + browser)" as UI
participant "Middleware" as MW
database "middleware_db\n(session_state)" as DB

note over UI
  **Client timers** (keychain / customer_app):
  ATM_IDLE_PROMPT_SECONDS = 120 → show dialog
  ATM_PROMPT_TIMEOUT_SECONDS = 60 → auto sign-out
end note

== Idle prompt ==

C -> UI : No input for 120 seconds
UI -> C : Modal: "Another transaction?"
note right of UI
  No Core Banking call.
  No idempotency key.
end note

alt Customer clicks **Yes, continue** within 60s

  C -> UI : Yes
  UI -> UI : POST /session/continue\n(credentials: same-origin)

  UI -> MW : POST /atm/session/continue\nX-Session-Token: <token>

  MW -> MW : sessions.touch(token)

  MW -> DB : SELECT session_state\nWHERE session_token = <token>
  DB --> MW : row

  alt Session valid (not past SESSION_TTL)

    MW -> DB : UPDATE last_active = now
    DB --> MW : OK

    MW --> UI : 200 OK\n{status: "ok"}
    UI --> C : Stay logged in;\nreset UI idle timer

    note right of MW
      Only **last_active** changes.
      JWT, balance, account fields unchanged.
      **Core Banking is not called.**
    end note

  else Missing or expired session

    MW --> UI : **401** Invalid or expired session
    UI --> C : Redirect to login

  end

else Customer clicks **No** or 60s elapse

  C -> UI : No / timeout
  UI -> MW : POST /atm/logout\nX-Session-Token
  MW -> DB : DELETE session row
  UI --> C : Signed out

end

@enduml
